data.description: BACK on MARKET -Please Show!!!!Sizes and measurements are approximate - Cute, Cute, Cute - Quaint Florida Cottage in Historic Millville.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath sits on a fenced corner lot, within moments to Downtown Panama City, 15 minutes to TAFB.  The home has beautiful and restored wood flooring, ceramic flooring, galley kitchen, dining/living, large bonus room currently used as an office and a large storage, laundry area.  The home has been well maintained.  Brand new roof thanks to Hurricane Michael, as well as a brand new privacy fence for the large backyard.
